flowchart LR
  User[Founder / Enterprise User] --> CF[CloudFront or Amplify]
  CF --> App[Web App]
  App --> Cognito[Cognito User Pool]
  App --> API[API Gateway HTTP API]
  API --> Lambda[Lambda API]
  Lambda --> DDB[DynamoDB Metadata]
  Lambda --> S3[S3 Evidence Bucket]
  Lambda --> EB[EventBridge]
  EB --> SQS[SQS Evidence Queue]
  SQS --> SFN[Step Functions]
  SFN --> Bedrock[Amazon Bedrock]
  SFN --> KB[Bedrock Knowledge Bases]
  Bedrock --> Guardrails[Bedrock Guardrails]
  SFN --> Package[S3 Audit Package]
  Package --> Custodian[Human Custodian Approval]
  API --> CW[CloudWatch Logs/Metrics]
  S3 --> Trail[CloudTrail]
